text: Kirovskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltymanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 62 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Iglino, 5 km from Kaltymanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Kirovskoye, Republic of Bashkortostan
